{"id":50,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":50,"title":"Chapter 47: Jesus Christ Blesses His Disciples","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 47","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 47"],["h1","Jesus Christ Blesses His Disciples"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_050_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p3"},"One day when the disciples were together fasting and praying, Jesus Christ came to them."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/27.1-2"},"3 Nephi 27:1–2"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_050_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p5"},"The disciples asked him what they should name the Church. Jesus said it should be named after him because it was his Church."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/27.3,7"},"3 Nephi 27:3, 7"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_050_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p7"},"Jesus explained to his disciples that Heavenly Father had sent him to earth to give his life for all people."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/27.14"},"3 Nephi 27:14"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_050_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p9"},"He said everyone who repents, is baptized in his name, and obeys his commandments will be held guiltless before Heavenly Father."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/27.16"},"3 Nephi 27:16"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_050_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p11"},"The Savior told his disciples to do the things they had seen him do. He had set the example for them."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/27.21"},"3 Nephi 27:21"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.f6"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_050_06.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p13"},"He also told them to write down what they had seen and heard so that others could know about it."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/27.23-25"},"3 Nephi 27:23–25"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.f7"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_050_07.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p15"},"Jesus asked his disciples what they would like from him. Nine of them wanted to be with him after their lives on earth had ended."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.1-2"},"3 Nephi 28:1–2"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.f8"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_050_08.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p17"},"Jesus promised them that when they were 72 years old, they would go to him in heaven."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.3"},"3 Nephi 28:3"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.f9"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_050_09.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p19"},"The other three disciples did not dare ask for what they wanted, but Jesus knew. They wanted to stay on the earth and teach the gospel until Jesus came again."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.5-6,9"},"3 Nephi 28:5–6, 9"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.f10"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_050_10.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p21"},"The Savior promised them that they would not suffer pain or sorrow and would not die. They would teach people the gospel until he returned."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.7-9"},"3 Nephi 28:7–9"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.f11"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_050_11.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p23"},"Jesus touched each disciple except the three who would stay on the earth. Then he left."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.12"},"3 Nephi 28:12"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.f12"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_050_12.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p25","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p25"},"The three disciples were taken to heaven, where they saw and heard many wonderful things. They were better able to understand the things of God."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p26","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p26"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.13,15"},"3 Nephi 28:13, 15"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.f13"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_050_13.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p27","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p27"},"Their bodies were changed so they would not die."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p28","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p28"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.15"},"3 Nephi 28:15"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.f14"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_050_14.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p29","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p29"},"The three disciples returned to earth and began preaching and baptizing."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p30","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p30"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.16,18"},"3 Nephi 28:16, 18"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.f15"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_050_15.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p31","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p31"},"Wicked Nephites threw the three disciples into prison and into deep pits, but God’s power helped them escape."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p32","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p32"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.19-20"},"3 Nephi 28:19–20"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.f16"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_050_16.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p33","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p33"},"When they were pushed into furnaces and into dens with wild animals, they were also protected by the power of God."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p34","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p34"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.21-22"},"3 Nephi 28:21–22"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.f17"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_050_17.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p35","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p35"},"The three disciples continued to preach the gospel of Jesus Christ to the Nephites. They are still preaching his gospel."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p36","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-47-jesus-christ-blesses-his-disciples.p36"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.23,27-29"},"3 Nephi 28:23, 27–29"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
